nodes.text: The Star Wars Publications Timeline was a media timeline by Allan Kausch published in Star Wars Insider 23 in the fall of 1994. The timeline covered the variety of Star Wars comics and novels that had been published by that time, spanning from Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi - Dark Lords of the Sith in "-4000 yrs" to the first three books of the Young Jedi Knights series in "+23 yrs."
